profile:
Established in l978, Nortown Paving & Construction Inc. has built a reputation for
excellence - specializing in all facets of asphalt paving, concrete work and interlocking
stone.
Nortown Paving & Construction Inc. is a family owned and operated business. Continuing 40 years of experience in the paving business.
Since the beginning, the Company has served Metropolitan of Toronto residents earning respect within the business as one of the most professional and personal companies in the
industry.
With industrial and residential size equipment, no job is to small or big for Nortown Paving & Construction Inc. We use heavy duty equipment for best results.
In April, 2004 Nortown Paving & Construction Inc. was chosen as the business of the week in Toronto.
Customers deal directly with the owners of Nortown Paving & Construction Inc. and each member of the staff has at least l0 years paving experience.
Nortown Paving & Construction Inc. is fully insured and carries a performance bond and is registered with the Ministry of Consumer and Commercial Relations.
Nortown Paving & Construction Inc. is a member of the Better Business Bureau and the Toronto Builders Association.

Our business is built on satisfied customers. All work carries a one year guarantee.

profile:
West York Paving Ltd. is a family owned and operated business that was established in 1965. We have been a leading force in the paving community and have been serving the City of Etobicoke, the City of Toronto and the surrounding GTA areas for over 45 years.
 
Mission Statement
Our dedication and commitment is to provide SUPERIOR CUSTOMER SERVICE through our outstanding professional integrity, our experienced staff, our competitive pricing and our exceptional workmanship. Our pledge to our customers is to establish trust through our work ethics. At West York Paving we promise to use ONLY the highest grade of raw materials, impressive State of the Art paving equipment and trucks to ensure that the FINISHED PRODUCT ALWAYS MEETS AND EXCEEDS THE CUSTOMERS SATISFACTION AND EXPECTATIONS.
 
Our impeccable reputation and image in the residential and commercial paving contractors business has been built on Our Mission statement. The proof is in our constant customer referrals and repeat business.
 
AWARD WINNING PAVING COMPANY YOU CAN TRUST! CHOSEN BY YOU!!! We are the proud Readers' Choice Awards Winner for 2010,2011 & 2012.
 
We are officially registered and proudly run as West York Paving Ltd. Company and we are also known as YORK WEST PAVING LTD. Both business names are run as one and the same. Our company’s name is synonymous with quality, value and excellent service. 
 
OUR GUARANTEE
At West York Paving Ltd., we individually design and engineer your driveway using the highest quality materials combining expertise with experience. Although residential driveways and commercial lot designs and projects may vary from client to client, specifications and skill are always guaranteed to be consistent; from the biggest job to the smallest.
West York Paving provides a full 12 month written guarantee with every contract.

profile:
Our Company
We at Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. are passionate about the work we do. Our commitment is to work with our clients to provide the best and most effective solution to complete the project in a safe and timely manner. We are dedicated to providing our clients a high level of customer satisfaction and accurate professional advice.
 
Our Health and Safety Policy
Our policy at Canturk Paving and General Contracting Ltd. is to provide and maintain a safe and healthy working environment. Compliance with Health and Safety regulations are outlined in the Health and Safety Policy of Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. Our employees are trained yearly and certified to ensure in reducing the risk of injuries in the workplace by following our policy.
 
Our Guarantee
We Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. construct each project using the highest quality materials, while providing the highest level of expertise and customer service. Even though each project varies from client to client, we provide quality service no matter the size of the project. Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. offers a written gurantee of 12 months from the date of completion.
services:
Asphalt Paving Services
Canturk Contracting Ltd. constructs asphalt pavements for property owners who desire affordable and high quality paving materials. Asphalt is durable and weather resistant, assuring maintenance and repairs are minimal. Unlike other poured materials asphalt is easy to install, therefore saving you hundreds of dollars in labor costs.

Our professional team at Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. provide the following asphalt services:

Parking Lots
Driveways
Walkways
Resurfacing
Patching
Speed Bumps
Trenches
Seal Coating
Crack Filling
Catch Basins
Line Marking
********************************
CONCRETE 
Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. offers a wide variety of concrete services. We are trained and skilled in all aspects of concrete projects. Concrete is being one of the oldest and most commonly used construction materials which possess countless benefits, along with being durable and relatively low maintenance. Concrete is reliable and has a long lifespan.

Our professional team at Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. provide the following concrete services:

Regular Concrete
Pattern Concrete
Colour Concrete
Standard Curbs
French Curbs
Garage Floors
Garbage Pads
Jewel Stone
********************************
Interlock Paving Services
Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. specializes in designing and implementing interlocking stone. We can construct a wide variety of outdoor spaces, including but not limited to driveways. Interlocking can make any outdoor space aesthetically pleasing with great quality stones. We work with our clients to design their layout and are also available to assist with selection of products and other aspects of the project.

Our professional team at Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. provide the following interlock services:

Interlocking Stone
Interlocking Steps
Interlocking Porches
Retaining Walls
Stone Waterfalls
Natural Flagstone
Masonry Repairs
Driveways
Walkways
Patios
Outdoor Kitchens (BBQs)
Fireplaces

"A Toronto Paving Company since 1967, Primo Paving provides nothing but professional paving services. We at Primo Paving stand behind our service and quality of work. 
Our commitment in the last half century is to provide extraordinary service through our highly experienced and trained staff. We commit to offering competitive pricing and professional workmanship. All of our services involve the use of the most current and heavy machinery in the industry to ensure proper response times and end results.
Part of being a leader in the paving community is due to Primo Paving's commitment to being diverse to our present and future clientèle. Through our various sizes of machinery, we ensure that no job is too big or too small that we will refuse. We commit to the ever changing construction industry through our safety, environmental and employment policies. Our employment and equipment safety policies, which we hold with high regard, are second to none in the industry.

We commit to using all environmental friendly materials which possess the highest grade and strongest end results. Our commitment to our employment policies ensure that our service through both our office and field staff reflect the professionalism and integrity of our everyday operations.

Primo Paving is a proud member of the better business bureau as well as many other organizations to ensure proper consumer relations."

Paving, Interlocking, Concrete
M.n.B. Paving Ltd. offers a full range of hardscaping services including interlocking, steps and walls, pool decks and surrounds, asphalt and concrete.

Commercial
We understand that you want to work with a company that cares as much about your property as you do. Here’s why you should consider M.n.B. as your partner:

Experienced

We have over 27 years of experience, helping homeowners and businesses create the landscape of their dreams. We’ve created the perfect design in all types of conditions and have the happy customers to prove it.

Our team is experienced in all aspects of landscape design and build projects, including interlocking stone, retaining walls, asphalt and concrete work, and putting the finishing touches on pools.

Professional

Using the best products on the market, backed by the latest technology and machines, our team is meticulous about your project. We prepare your site, carefully perform the installation, and always clean up after ourselves. Our workers conduct themselves with the utmost professionalism, because we know we’re working where you live.

Quality, built to last

We’re committed to creating the environment you’ve been dreaming about, one that will improve your curb appeal, and leave a lasting impression. Each project is closely monitored for quality, and the company owner is involved in your project from start to finish to ensure your satisfaction.

M.n.B. Paving is a member of the Better Business Bureau with an A+ rating.

profile:
With decades of experience in the industry, our experts at Tikal Paving LTD have a reputation for designing and building beautiful, durable projects. We are your one-stop-shop for a variety of outdoor installation and repair services whether your needs are residential, commercial, industrial, or municipal.

Each project is carefully engineered to suit your individual needs and executed by our skilled and licensed contractors. Our team takes attention to detail seriously and uses top-quality materials for finished products that are as durable as they are visually appealing. That’s why any project completed by Tikal Paving LTD is guaranteed for one year. Our range of services includes landscaping, asphalt, concrete, interlocking brick, and snow plowing.

Our approach to outdoor projects is in our name; Tikal Paving. Tikal National Park is a 576 km² area in Guatemala that perfectly combines natural wonders with architectural feats that have survived enduring the elements for centuries. We believe the harmony between stunning natural landscaping and durable architectural elements is not only achievable, but a requirement for a functional and enjoyable space.

Not only do we guarantee superior workmanship, but we are also dedicated to providing the best customer service in the area. Get in touch with us to discuss your project and we will be happy to answer all your questions and provide a free quote.

profile:
Welcome to Nathan's Asphalt Service. We clean and prepare the driveway by removing all the weeds and filling the cracks with asphalt. We then blow off the dust so we can poor sealer on the driveway and brush it on to protect the driveway from cracks and water damage. This allows the driveway to look new and protected, leaving it with a nice black matte finish. 

In order to seal concrete, we start by blowing off and then use a 3300 PSI Power washer to clean the dirt, stains, and grime off the concrete. Then we allow it to dry for 24 hours. Once dry, we use Seal King concrete sealer to rejuvenate the concrete's colour and to protect it from stains and cracking. Finally, we use a seal grip to protect it from being slippery.

For sealing interlock, we start by blowing off and then use a 3300 PSI Power washer to remove weeds and clean the stones. Then, after letting it dry for 24 hours, we pour polymeric and spread it into the cracks to fill them. The sand is lightly soaked to get hard overnight and then sealed the next day with Seal King to rejuvenate and bring back the colour of the stones while protecting them from sun damage and sinking.
